title: Lockheed delivered fraction of missile defense interceptors

Published By: Reuters - Technology - Today 
WASHINGTON (Reuters) - Lockheed Martin Corp delivered only three of 44 interceptors for the THAAD missile defense system in fiscal year 2015...
